Rosneft Bank Unit to Handle Utilities Payments, Kommersant Says

-- B y   Y u l i y a   F e d o r i n o v a
-- 
2011-09-02T04:07:06Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-02/rosneft-bank-unit-to-handle-utilities-payments-kommersant-says.html
OAO Rosneft’s bank unit plans to
become the sole payment center for  Russia ’s utilities, replacing
OAO Alfa Bank,  Kommersant  reported today, citing unidentified
people familiar with the plan.  The Russian Regional Development Bank, as the Rosneft unit
is called, may get access to a market with 1 trillion rubles
($34.5 billion) in annual turnover, the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Yuliya Fedorinova in Moscow at 
 yfedorinova@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
John Viljoen at 
 jviljoen@bloomberg.net  